                            "title": "Unknown Sitter",
                            "description": "<p>We don’t know the sitter, but we can guess his position and personality. Obviously affluent, a little flamboyant, he made some concession to Protestant modesty by wearing a simple black suit. He might have been a Burgomaster, the Dutch term for a city leader.</p>"
