                            "title": "An exotic menagerie",
                            "description": "<p>Peacock, leopard, camel, and parrots all take center stage for the king.  It is a rare set of animals to have gathered all together and an example of exoticism—a European understanding of an unknown East made vague and generic with embellishments that were not native to Europe.</p>"
