                            "title": "Words of Gratitude",
                            "description": "<p>“Goya gives thanks to his friend Arrieta for the expert care with which he saved his life from an acute and dangerous illness which he suffered at the close of the year 1819 when he was 73 years old. He painted it in 1820.”</p>"
