                            "title": "A Pebble",
                            "description": "<p>A pebble found on a beach inspired Moore to create <em>Warrior with Shield</em>. &nbsp;Its shape reminded Moore of the stump of a leg amputated at the hip. &nbsp;He writes, “Just as Leonardo says somewhere in his notebooks that a painter can find a battle scene in the lichen marks on a wall, so this [a pebble] gave me the start of <em>The Warrior</em> idea.”</p>"
