                            "attachments": [],
                            "description": "<p>The uncomfortable-loooking man in question is Innocent X, who was the pope from 1644 until his death in 1655. He was a politically shrewd and unscrupulous man whose actions contradicted the name he chose as pope: Innocent.</p>",
                            "title": "Who Is He?"
