                            "title": "Ultimate Flex Space",
                            "description": "<p>Occasions dictate outfits, but in a salon they also influenced furniture arrangements. Recitals, card games, and other gatherings all called for different types of tables and seating. That was the beauty of a salon: in a house full of rooms dedicated to specific purposes, a salon was designed to be the ultimate flex space. </p>"
