                            "title": "A Japanese Cinderella Story",
                            "description": "<p>Chūjōhime, an eighth-century noblewoman, fled to a temple to escape her wicked stepmother. Legend has it that Amida Buddha visited her there and wove a splendid tapestry of the Pure Land. Many copies were made, including this one.&nbsp;</p>"
