                            "title": "Urdu Poetry",
                            "description": "<p>Rhymed couplets on the back of the painting are written in Dakani Urdu, a language that incorporates elements of Persian, Arabic, Sanskrit, and Indian regional languages, attesting to the cosmopolitan nature of the Deccani courts.</p>"
