                            "title": "A Table for Display",
                            "description": "<p>You wouldn’t eat at this table, or play cards, or much of anything really. You put stuff on it as a showcase, perhaps potpourri (a bowl with aromatic scents), a candlestick, a vase, a flashy box, or a precious bronze sculpture. </p>"
