                            "title": "The Battle for Conservation",
                            "description": "<p>Even with an extra leg, the table struggled to support its original marble top. Also, the gilding was prone to flaking off; new gold leaf was applied three different times. Mia restored the table and added wall-mounted supports to prop it up.</p>"
