                                    "meta": "From _Pride and Prejudice_, Warner Brothers Cinema, 2005.",
                                    "description": "<p>Kiera Knightly, as Lady Elizabeth, admires <i>Veiled Vestal</i></p>",
                                    "thumbnail": "http://cdn.dx.artsmia.org/thumbs/tn_2014_TDX_MIAArtStories_004.jpg"
