                                    "description": "<p>These 19<sup>th</sup>-century fan cases would have held the same types of folding fans that are featured in the wallpaper scenes. Fan cases, China, 19<sup>th</sup> century, silk, embroidery, metallic threads, glass beads, The Miscellaneous Works of Art Purchase Fund, 91.5.6 (left) and 91.5.5 (right)</p>"
