                                    "image_id": "100629_mia341_161000",
                                    "description": "<p>Making noise on New Year’s goes way back, well beyond the wallpaper partiers and the folks in this detail of a painting, ringing in the New Year with drums, cymbals, and firecrackers. Such paintings were themselves displayed as part of the festivities.</p>"
