                            "title": "Copperheads",
                            "description": "<p>The snakes are venomous copperheads, per the dots on their heads. “Copperhead” also referred to Northern sympathizers with the Confederate cause. Anna, Illinois, where the Kirkpatricks lived, was full of them—a vipers’ den. Here, the snakes have imprisoned a Northern soldier, yet the Union won the war. Another jab.</p>"
