                            "attachments": [],
                            "title": "No Camera?",
                            "description": "<p>This image lacks the fundamental elements of a typical photograph. There was no camera. No subject or composing. And no development of the picture in a darkroom. Throw (C-918) only meets the definition of photography because it uses light-sensitive, photographic paper.</p>"
