                            "attachments": [],
                            "description": "<p>The lid shows the artist in his studio, surrounded by tools of the trade—an anvil and hammer on the forge as well as a heating cauldron and box of chasing punches beside him on the table.</p>",
                            "title": "Portrait of the Artist"
