                            "title": "Signs of the Times",
                            "description": "<p>Not everything carved into the desk was a tool. Take these trade symbols, displayed outside stores in the 1800s to quickly note the services rendered inside. The glove on Howard’s desk was the trade sign for, you guessed it, a glove maker.</p>"
