                            "attachments": [],
                            "title": "It's Complicated",
                            "description": "<p>Several fairly isolated social groups come together in this tense scene: a well-heeled middle class, the police, and marijuana-supporting hippies, not to mention the folks just passing through. The staged image brings them altogether in a single, compressed moment so we can closely examine the forces at play.</p>"
