                            "attachments": [],
                            "title": "Pics or It Didn’t Happen",
                            "description": "<p>The phrase “pics or it didn’t happen” could be the caption for this photo, which celebrates a forgotten moment in local Vancouver history. Its grand size proclaims, “Look at what’s happening. &nbsp;Remember it. It is important.” &nbsp; Focusing on lost histories is a common subject in contemporary art, as artists reveal how our usual ways of processing events can overlook important moments of history.</p>"
