                            "attachments": [],
                            "title": "War and Peace",
                            "description": "<p>Flanking the main gate are two archdukes of Austria, one whose armor peeks out from behind his robe, the other in princely robes—a lesson to future princes that they will attain honor only if they are strong enough to keep the peace and wise enough to administer justice equally to rich and poor alike. </p>"
