                            "attachments": [],
                            "title": "Griffons",
                            "description": "<p>A griffon is half lion (king of the beasts) and half eagle (king of the birds), making it the king of all creatures. Naturally, Maximilian chose it to represent himself, as his personal emblem, and there are many on the arch. The four atop columns hold symbols of his rule. This one holds a banner that says, <em>Halt Mass</em>, the emperor's motto, meaning \"Keep within bounds\"—moderation in the use of his power. </p>"
