                            "title": "Banners",
                            "description": "<p>Ancient Roman emperors and kings waded into battle accompanied by banners bearing eagles and dragons. Displayed here, they reinforce Maximilian's invented ancestry, suggesting that his ties to the throne of the Holy Roman Empire are long and legitimate, stretching back into antiquity.  </p>"
