                            "title": "Stop Action",
                            "description": "<p>Hundreds of drawings were photographed and pieced together by Kentridge to give a sense of movement—the “stop action” film technique. By showing erasures and redrawing, he emphasizes dramatic change, even an optimism about the possibility of transformation in South Africa.</p>"
