                            "attachments": [],
                            "title": "The Megaphone",
                            "description": "<p>Megaphones “indicate what needs to be heard or seen, outside of oneself,” Kentridge says. &nbsp;A drawing of a megaphone emitting sound appears throughout the video, a recurring motif since Kentridge’s first animated film, <em>Monuments </em>(1991).</p>"
