                            "title": "Britain",
                            "description": "<p>The inscription above this couple phonetically reads, \"<em>Biritaniya</em>\"—Britain, or Brittannia as it was sometimes called. The painter had never seen a British person, so instead he turned to illustrations from a Dutch map circulating through Japan at this time. Today, that map survives only in grainy photographs taken before World War II. </p>"
