                            "title": "Modeling",
                            "description": "<p>The painter did not just paint Europeans based on European images. He also adopted European painting techniques not used in Japan. With the exception of the East Asian figures, he depicted all the rest using modeling—the use of shading to suggest three-dimensionality. </p>"
