                            "title": "Peru",
                            "description": "<p>No Japanese person in the 1640s had seen a Peruvian. Few, if any, had even heard of Peru. The painter of our handscroll turned to a picture on the Dutch map captioned \"Chilenses et Peruiani\" (Chile and Peru). He labeled the pair \"Peruvians\" but he left off the \"Chileans.\" </p>"
