                            "title": "Americans",
                            "description": "<p>This picture of a couple wearing clothes decorated with colorful feathers is captioned \"America,\" a word and place the Japanese could not fathom. No such image exists on the Dutch map, so where did this image of native North Americans come from? </p>"
